      "content": "hey so i have this insanely bad headache out of nowhere like its the worst one i ever had and i noticed my eye looks a bit weird on one side like my face is slightly off. is this just a really bad migraine? i have some old sumatriptan in my cabinet, can i just take a couple of those to make it go away?",
